title: MONDAY 3/15 - Drew Brees calls is a career
itunes:title: MONDAY 3/15 - Drew Brees calls is a career
description:
Quarterback Drew Brees(0:08) makes it official, ending his hall of fame career. The free agency frenzy is underway, but a couple guys staying put...Running back Aaron Jones(1:25) re-signing with the Packers, while Kyle Juszczyk (1:52) remains in San Francisco. The Bears lock up Mario Edwards (2:12), plus a couple trades taking place on Sunday (2:19)
